    "en": {
      "title": "Landing of 'Super Diesel' begins",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Power and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said this afternoon (25) that due to a problem in banking affairs, the landing of the 'Super Diesel' ship, which was supposed to land yesterday, was delayed and started its disembarkation this afternoon. said.",
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekera further said that another diesel ship is scheduled to reach Colombo tonight and its diesel stock will start unloading tomorrow morning as scheduled."
      ],
